"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/62706","Ministry of Justice","false","2014-06-26","<p>There have been no non-disclosure or compromise agreements included as part of the departure packages of the Trust Chief Executives who have taken early retirement. The terms of departure for other former Trust staff were agreed through their own local arrangements<em>. </em></p>","Kenilworth and Southam","Jeremy Wright",,"2014-06-26T10:32:52.9851501Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/62706/answer","Biography information for Jeremy Wright","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/62706/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/62706/answer",,,,,"54","Justice","Justice","2014-06-18","Probation Trusts","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Justice, how much has been spent on non-disclosure or compromise agreements for former employees of probation trusts since 1 January 2014.","false","Biography information for Sadiq Khan","Tooting","Sadiq Khan","201230"
